rigins in statistical mechanics, condensed\nmatter and dynamical systems by revisiting Bak, Tang and Wiesenfeld's original\npapers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2015 09:45:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-27"}
