 to either a strong\noutflow (due to a propeller effect) or a trapped disk (with limited/no outflow)\nin the inner regions of the accretion flow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2015 13:28:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-03"}
